    "The most commonly used sample unit was clinical notes or reports (34/93, 37%) followed by sentences and papers or abstracts (21/93, 23%).",
    "Sample size ranges also varied widely by unit type, as would be expected.",
    "The smallest clinical notes or reports sample used a scant 17 documents [26], but this was likely a larger sample than the smallest reported sentence sample size of 100 [27].",
